  <md:title>Radioactive Decay</md:title>
  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list>
<item>Recognize common modes of radioactive decay</item>
<item>Identify common particles and energies involved in nuclear decay reactions</item>
<item>Write and balance nuclear decay equations</item>
<item>Calculate kinetic parameters for decay processes, including half-life</item>
<item>Describe common radiometric dating techniques</item>
</list></md:abstract>
